{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_09_01",
  "title": "神崎莉央 1話 じっと見ないでちょうだい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――東京シーサイド　タイアップ依頼を引き受けた後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After accepting the Tokyo Seaside tie-up request.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、打ち合わせは終わったのに\n莉央さんにだけ残ってもらって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to keep you here‚ Rio-san‚\nbut I need to talk to you about something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "いいのよ。それで私に話しておきたいことって何？\n……やっぱり、東京シーサイドのCM撮影の件？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s fine. So what did you want to talk about?\n…It’s about the Tokyo Seaside commercial shoot‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1999998093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。リーダーの莉央さんとは話しておきたいと思って\n今回、俺も橋本さんも同行出来なくて、迷惑をかけます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I wanted to talk to you‚ Rio-san‚ as the leader.\nThis time‚ neither Hashimoto-san nor I can go with you‚ so it's going to be a bit of a burden.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3999998093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "貴方が気に病むことはないわ。星見プロは忙しいもの\n貴方のいない現場にも、慣れなきゃいけないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry about it. Hoshimi Pro is busy.\nWe have to get used to working on site without you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.166666476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "本当にすみません。マネージャーを増やさないとですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m really sorry. We need to increase the number of managers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9889107189,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないで。それに、どんなにいい人がいても\n貴方のかわりにはならないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry about it. And besides‚ no matter how good someone is‚\nthey can’t replace you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9999998093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　それって、どういう意味ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? What do you mean by that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.249456354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "……ええと、貴方みたいな世話好きで\nおせっかいな人なんて、他にいないって意味よ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ I mean‚ there’s no one else out there\nwho's as caring and meddlesome as you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9666682561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "だから勘違いはしないでちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So don't get the wrong idea!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4350342235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい……すみません……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-okay… I'm sorry…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6428560537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "……話が脱線したわね。本題は何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve gotten off track. What were you going to say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.8439897499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうでした。当日、俺が立ち会えないかわりに\n何か下準備が出来ないかと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. I was wondering if there’s anything I can do to prepare beforehand‚\nsince I won’t be there on the day…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7000003179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね。私だけでも、事前に現場を確認出来たら\n当日の役に立つかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re right. It might be helpful if I could check the site beforehand‚\neven if I’m alone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.8000023525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "現場の確認ですか……\nじゃあ良かったら、今から俺と行きませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The site checking…\nWould you like to go with me now then?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.1666690191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　今から？　二人で？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Now? The two of us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6835793934,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4363.740889200002,
          "startTime": 90.0473202826
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4683.08905340001,
          "startTime": 90.3666684468
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.7973202826
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.7973202826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅん……思っていたより、ずっと広いわね\n景色もいいし、綺麗な映像が撮れそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… It's much bigger than I expected.\nThe scenery is great. We should be able to get some beautiful footage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.3333438238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "何より、開園前の貸し切り状態だから\nじっくり見て回れそうだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And best of all‚ it’s closed to the public right now‚\nso we can take our time looking around.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9333428066,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.4207977735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "あら、この海水プール、凄いわ！\n水の透明度が、よそのプールと全然違う！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my‚ this seawater pool is amazing!\nThe water's transparency is completely different from other pools!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8000176114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.5753099564
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "最新の設備で、常に綺麗な状態を維持管理しているって\nパンフレットに書いてありました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The pamphlet says they use the latest equipment\nto constantly maintain and manage the pool in a clean state.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.166684278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、気に入ったみたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem to like it‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.2402761582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.9407070124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなことないわ。このプールを背景に歩くと\nいい画になりそうって思っただけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-it’s not like that. I just thought it would make a good shot\nto walk with this pool as the background.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2333509447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "私達らしさを出すならダンスを織り交ぜてもいいわね\nねぇ、CMではどんな衣装を着るの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It could be good to incorporate some dancing to show off our style.\nBy the way‚ what kind of outfits are we wearing for the commercial?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.1000176114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.1544254902
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "当日の衣装は、水着風のステージ衣装です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The costumes for the day are swimsuit-style stage outfits.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.1544254902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、そうよね。プールだし\n……水着で変なポーズとか要求されないでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that makes sense. It is a pool‚ after all.\nThey're not going to ask us to do weird poses in swimsuits‚ are they?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.7333509447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに大丈夫だと思いますけど……\nそうですね、事前に確認しておきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think they wouldn't…\nBut I'll make sure to check beforehand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.9525547625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.2455912394
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "私達だけでも大丈夫だとは言ったものの、妙なノリの\nプロデューサーらしいし、多少不安はあるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I said we'd be fine on our own‚ but I’m a little worried\nsince he seems like the type of producer to get carried away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.9638679626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.7173599047
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "その不安を少しでも減らせるように頑張ります\n衣装、もう完成してるので見てみます？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll do my best to alleviate your concerns.\nThe costumes are already finished‚ would you like to see them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.4000043871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
