      "text": "用意がいいわね\n出来ることは全部やっておきたいし、見せてもらえる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're well-prepared.\nI want to be as prepared as possible‚ so show me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.7333377204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
