      "text": "（……そういうことじゃなくて）\n（遊んでリラックスしてもらうつもりだったんだけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…That’s not what I meant.）\n（I was hoping you could relax and have some fun.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.3999972662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
